<p><strong>标题：</strong>SCP-1139-JP 电子的歌姬<br />
<strong>作者：</strong>©︎<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/falsehood" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3979506); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3979506&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607958799" alt="falsehood" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3979506)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/falsehood" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3979506); return false;">falsehood</a></span><br />
<strong>作成年：</strong>2018<br />
<strong>原文：*<a href="http://scp-jp.wikidot.com/scp-1139-jp" target="_blank">http://scp-jp.wikidot.com/scp-1139-jp</a><br /></strong>译者：**<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/irenekara" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6058545); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6058545&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607958799" alt="IreneKara" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6058545)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/irenekara" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6058545); return false;">IreneKara</a></span></p>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
</div>
</div>
